How to implement inheritance in JAVA?


By using extends and implements keywords

1. Normal Class/Concrete Class(NC)
2. Abstract Class(AC)
3. Interface Class(IC)


super/parent/base class		    keyword			sub/child/derived class
		
	Normal class				extends 			  Normal Class
	Abstract class				extends 			  Normal Class
	Interface class			   implements 			  Normal Class
	
	Normal class				extends 			  Abstract class
	Abstract class				extends 			  Abstract class
	Interface class			   implements 			  Abstract class
	
	Normal class				  NO 			      Interface class	
	Abstract class				  NO			      Interface class	
	Interface class			   extends 			  	  Interface class	